6 National Circuit is  located in the heart of the Parliamentary Triangle offering close proximity to Parliament House, the Finance and Treasury offices, Attorney Generals offices and The Department of Prime Minister and Cabinet. Located only minutes from the CBD, Kingston and Manuka this address offers access to various amenities. Surrounded by some of Barton's best cafes and eateries you have no shortage of great coffee and lunch time snacks. 

6 National is an 'A-grade boutique office building with basement car parking and excellent EOT facilities. 

Available for lease is 521sqm* on the ground floor,
the tenancy has an immaculate near new fit-out in place which contains 33 open plan work stations, a generous size board room and a great break out kitchenette area for staff.
